body:
For two days i have been trying to start LoL client but it keeps crashing. When I click on LoL, the only thing that happens is that the LoL icon pops up, if i click on the icon, its background turns dark and I get a message saying "PVP.net kernel has stopped working." And if I let it load instead of clicking over the popped up icon, after a certain time it shows me a message with a title that says "RADS error"
I have been looking for a solution for this for 2 days, tried everything I saw in internet, those worked for me earlier though, but this time its not working for me. I tried admin mode, tried changing my dns server address, tried changing compatibility mode, edited system.cfg file. But my client keeps crashing. 
Please, help me. {{champion:32}}
